            <description><![CDATA[【👂🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%89%93%E7%94%B5%E8%AF%9D%E6%80%BB%E5%90%AC%E4%B8%8D%E6%B8%85%E5%BE%88%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%90%AC%E5%8A%9B%E5%B7%B2%E5%8F%97%E6%8D%9F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%89%93%E7%94%B5%E8%AF%9D%E6%80%BB%E5%90%AC%E4%B8%8D%E6%B8%85%E5%BE%88%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%90%AC%E5%8A%9B%E5%B7%B2%E5%8F%97%E6%8D%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#打电话总听不清很可能听力已受损#</span></a>】不知是不是耳机戴多了，阿卫常觉得自己一接打电话就是“聋的传人”，大家会吗……<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[跪了]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_guile-a8a737d3a0.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>听力受损是不可逆的，如果出现持续耳鸣、电话中听不清对话等情况，一定要去查查听力哦~<br><br>经常出入噪音场所会损害听力吗？老年人听力下降不需要干预？新买的助听器需要调试吗？会越戴越聋？这里一文说清👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（健康中国）<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E8%A6%81%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E7%9A%84%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E5%90%AC%E5%8A%9B%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E8%A6%81%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E7%9A%84%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E5%90%AC%E5%8A%9B%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#一定要了解的保护听力方法#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hndlklgucwj20m80m80w4.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hndlklit9ij20m80m8gor.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hndlklip7qj20m80m8adl.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hndlklly3aj20m80m80vg.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sin